This folder contains the code which is going to classify the emails based on their content.

After the emails are classified they are forwarded to Departmet heads from the company email.

For now there are few categories of emails as per the scale of project: 
 1.Accounts
 2.Sales
 3.CRM
 4.Service
 5.Purchases
 6.Others(Alerts,Advertisement etc)
 
I have taken pre-trained model, BERT(Bidirectional Encoder Represetations from Transformers) is a NLP model developed by Google.

I have trained the model on dataset containing set of emails. Dataset is taken from Kaggle
